overview: The Kings of Wrestling must face the combined might of Mike Quackenbush, Skayde, Jigsaw and the YLC champ, Shane Storm, in relevos atomicos action. Chuichiro Arai challenges for the ICW-ICWA Tex-Arkana Television Championship! Milano Collection AT takes on Chris Hero in singles action and Jervis Cottonbelly meets Crossbones.
title: Chikara: Little Creatures
